{
  "texts": [
    "The ability to adapt existing business models is another critical factor in determining digital transformation success (Berman, 2012; Remane et al., 2017).",
    "The value propositions and customer relationships are central to SMEs' business models.",
    "Changes made to customer touchpoints, value propositions, and the optimization of customer interactions and collaborations significantly affect the business model and digital transformation.",
    "Internal and external factors affecting SMEs' digital transformation were thoroughly categorized by Tarutė et al. (2018).",
    "They focused on how SMEs adapt their business models and adopt new technologies."
  ]
}